examples.en: I was totally unprepared for the challenge which faced me.
I am unprepared to take on such a responsibility.
They were unprepared to accept the conditions of the contract.
Being taken by surprise, they were totally unprepared for resistance.
He was unprepared for such a strong counter campaign by opponents of the legislative bill.
We were unprepared for the apparition that confronted us.
A first menstruation can be somewhat scary for girls who are unprepared.
